{"type": "article", "id": 18080, "title": "丝绸椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-26T07:20:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144336puQ1tMbdUSOBIGVF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是造作在今年推出的丝绸椅，来自意大利的设计师 Luca Nichetto。椅子的特色在于帆船型的座位面，更贴合人的身体。此外，座椅的边缘处用高光提亮，突出了柔和的线条。椅子整体都用一种颜色，有松石绿、石灰绿、红、白、黄 5 种颜色可选，售价 664 元，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/e/z/silkchair\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144334npmfGcgSt3RU9Pdw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33222037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144334AJX4vMljkQPEbYxq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144335oN1UMJkRup8F2fi5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144335QlthOY8cB6oe41CU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}